    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one! It looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is literally flawless. It drives like a total dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. You really have to see it in person to believe how clean it is! Perfect for someone who wants that brand-new feel. Let me know if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
