    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s engineering peak. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system for razor-sharp throttle response. The power is managed by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Every mechanical interface, from the subframe bushings to the cooling system, remains in flawless synchronization. This vehicle offers a pure, high-revving analog experience in concours-grade condition, with zero deferred maintenance and impeccable chassis rigidity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
