    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for showroom excellence. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, appearing as though it was just delivered from the factory. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no swirls, chips, or imperfections, complemented by pristine alloy wheels and factory-fresh trim. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery retains its original scent and supple texture, with every control and electronic feature functioning with crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, benefiting from a comprehensive, no-expense-spared maintenance history performed exclusively by master technicians. With exceptionally low mileage and a driving experience that is as tight and responsive as day one, this is a rare opportunity for the most discerning buyer to own a piece of automotive perfection. Includes all original documentation, spare keys, and a flawless service record.",
      "price": 48500.0,
