    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been babied since day one, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh interior smell. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been cared for with a lot of love, this is definitely the one for you!",
      "price": 44900.0,
