    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1997 Porsche 911 (993) Carrera, the final evolution of the air-cooled era. This specimen features the 3.6L flat-six engine equipped with the Varioram induction system for optimized mid-range torque, paired with the legendary G50 six-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is impeccably preserved, maintaining its original kinematic toe rear suspension geometry and factory-spec dampening. Every component, from the heat exchangers to the valve covers, remains free of seepage. The exterior retains its factory-applied finish with deep luster, while the interior shows no signs of bolster wear or UV degradation. A mechanically synchronized masterpiece for the serious enthusiast.",
